reviewText: T​his course requires you to purchase a certificate to advance in the material.

Dr. Craig Gurney provided excellent leadership in the way he put this course together and delivered it.  He genuinely believes in promoting critical thinking and cares about this subject matter.  I came away with a stronger level of confidence to engage in the conversation around displacement caused by unchecked gentrification.If I ever have the opportunity to take another course from Dr. Gurney, I'll sign up in a heartbeat.
Excellently structured and and helpful in pointing out further resources for students as well as providing further reading.
it was really an inspiring course!
